      <div class="col-md-10 col-lg-10 col-md-offset-1 col-lg-offset-1 text-center">   


          <h1 class="title">About Us</h1>
          <br>
          <h3>Our Mission</h3>
          <p>Finding books online should be as natural as wandering through a bookstore. There was no service out there that combines curated book lists with book previews. So we made Stacks 'n Stacks, a site that quickly lets readers browse quality books.</p>

          <h3>Our Tech</h3>
          <p> We leverage the Goodreads API to collect lists of user-curated books, and then use the Google Books Viewer API to present previews of each book to users. Stacks 'n Stacks is a Ruby on Rails App that uses jQuery to provide a seamless user experience and AJAX to make asynchronous calls to our database of books.</p>

